&lt;p&gt;This is an ideal role for a tax leader who wants to shape a function rather than inherit one, and who is energized by the operational rigor and strategic complexity of preparing a growth company for life as a public company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Checkr&#39;s global tax strategy across direct and indirect tax, including federal, state, local, and international jurisdictions, and build the function, team, and vendor ecosystem to support it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the quarterly and annual income tax provision, including documentation, disclosures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee all direct tax matters, including income tax compliance, transfer pricing, R&amp;amp;D credits, and tax attribute planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own indirect tax strategy and compliance, including sales and use tax&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Corporate Development on M&amp;amp;A tax due diligence, deal structuring, entity rationalization and post-close integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the trusted tax advisor across Legal, Accounting, FP&amp;amp;S, and Treasury on entity structuring, ETR forecasting, cash tax planning and intercompany&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare the tax function for public company readiness, including SOX-compliant processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years of progressive tax experience, including a combination of Big 4 and in-house roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in U.S. federal and state income tax, ASC 740, and indirect tax compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading the tax provision process end-to-end, including coordination with external auditors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience supporting or leading tax workstreams in M&amp;amp;A transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong cross-functional collaboration skills, particularly with Legal, Accounting, and FP&amp;amp;A&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPA, JD, or Master&#39;s in Taxation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An A-player mindset with a strong bias for action: you raise the bar, move with urgency, stay resilient through ambiguity, and take ownership to deliver meaningful outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
