&lt;li&gt;Partner with RevOps Technologies, Customer Marketing, and Account Management to build signal based automation and agentic upsell campaigns, grounded in sales process&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain data hygiene and process discipline in Salesforce across post-sales objects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales Ops, Analytics, and RevOps Technologies to integrate data sources and deliver ad hoc analysis that informs the post-sales operating cadence&lt;/li&gt;
