&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and a bias for action: you turn data into clear, actionable recommendations for GTM leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An A-player mindset with a strong bias for action: you raise the bar, move with urgency, stay resilient through ambiguity, and take ownership to deliver meaningful outcomes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
